org.usfirst.frc.team2791.robot

Class RobotMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usfirst.frc.team2791.robot.RobotMap

  • public class RobotMap
extends java.lang.Object
    The RobotMap is a mapping from the ports sensors and actuators are wired into to a variable name. This provides flexibility changing wiring and makes checking the wiring easier.
    There is a Google Sheet with all wiring and pneumatic related information.
    Author:
    team2791: See Robot.java for contact info
